block main
    section.grid.grid-cols-3.gap-4.container.pb-14
        .about-image.col-span-1
            img(src="./images/image-about-1.png", alt="alt")
        .about-content.col-span-2
            .content-main.p-20.flex.flex-col.gap-4 
                .content-title.flex.gap-2.items-center
                    ion-icon(name="bag").p-2.bg-pink.rounded-full.text-white.font-medium
                    span.text-sm.text-pink.font-medium This Week's 
                h3.content-header.text-third.font-bold.text-h3 Online shopping includes both buying things online. 
                h3.content-body.text-third.font-normal.text-h2.tracking-widest.leading-7 Salesforce B2C Commerce can help you create unified, intelligent digital commerce experiences — both online and in the store. 
                .content-footer.grid.grid-cols-2.gap-4 
                    span.text-sm.tracking.leading-5.text-gray Empower your sales teams with industry tailored solutions that support manufacturers as they go digital, and adapt to changing markets & customers faster by creating new business.    
                    span.text-sm.tracking.leading-5.text-gray Salesforce B2B Commerce offers buyers the seamless, self-service experience of online shopping with all the B2B    
